      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and functions as a dependable daily driver, though it clearly shows the effects of its age and mileage. Mechanically, it remains solid and starts up without issue, but the exterior has several cosmetic flaws, including a small dent on the rear passenger door and various paint chips and scratches across the body. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and some staining from regular use. While it isn't a showpiece, it is a functional and honest car for someone looking for basic transportation.",
