      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and demonstrating consistent mechanical reliability, it offers a refined and composed driving experience. The exterior retains its professional aesthetic integrity, while the interior remains preserved in commendable condition. Fully inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety, this automobile stands as a testament to quality engineering and responsible prior ownership.",
